{"tid":613390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"00後大陸化係因為老豆老母係70後","createTime":"2018-04-01T15:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T12:52:27.000Z","uid":25643,"like":207,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e36dea20bfc4390dab676115dd4729b64b50eb","tid":613390,"uid":25643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"據我觀察<br />\n<br />\n其實70後去到80頭呢班人嘅本土意識好弱<br />\n<br />\n政治冷感比例偏高﹐對支那唔太反感<br />\n<br />\n我識好多70後都成日講一日最衰都係佔中<br />\n<br />\n開口埋口支那強大了要學蝗語<br />\n<br />\n好多時同仔女講普通話唔講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n00後就係呢班人嘅仔女﹐再加上雙非溝淡<br />\n<br />\n耳濡目染下支那化﹐睇支那節目追支那明星講支那潮語<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅希望在於10後﹐因為雙非潮已經停咗<br />\n<br />\n而且經歷過雨革魚革﹐身土不二嘅80後自然會好好教育10後<br />\n<br />\n再之後90後教育嘅仔女20後亦會有保證<br />\n<br />\n當年70後唔夠60後爭上位﹐團結意識又唔及80後<br />\n<br />\n00後若果唔痛定思痛﹐<br />\n<br />\n注定同老竇老母70後一樣﹐<br />\n<br />\n成為塌陷嘅一代﹐香港嘅毒瘤﹐被其他世代鄙視"},{"pid":"e06bdf000164681aadf386ede421ccf6678c3917","tid":613390,"uid":1159,"like":118,"dislike":2,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"90後嘅仔女已經開始陸續出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc22470eae93bdd395e31f6cc8795d89bb3f0e5","tid":613390,"uid":11148,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"將來80,90後再加10後前後夾擊00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c3214af2a7a309d7735d037f9d10da349a280e","tid":613390,"uid":81575,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"點解我識嘅70後同你嗰批咁唔同?<br />\n<br />\n你嗰班係咪支那70後?"},{"pid":"7c89748af9f377df621a6506f540165f5c13ff74","tid":613390,"uid":57705,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed82d699ff71f6829ab79ac46037592fc60f0f24","tid":613390,"uid":132289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0